text: Chowdhury Harunur Rashid is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Chittagong-11. ==Career== Rashid was elected to parliament from Chittagong-11 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1986. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:Living people Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Chowdhury Harunur Rashid
